author: bnicholes
msg: Use getcwdpath() rather than getcwd() in apr_filepath_get() to make sure that
the resulting path includes a volume name.

author: bnicholes
msg: Missing a space between each missing item in the file info and the NULL as
the last argument to the apr_pstrcat() so that it doesn't run off the end.

author: rbb
msg: Make sure that when we print the string in test_localstr we get the
time in the PST timezone.  This way, we can be sure that the test will
succeed against the hard-coded string, which is in PST.

author: bnicholes
msg: If the platform does not have other child functionality then don't enable any
of the other child tests.  Otherwise the tests don't compile.
